title: Nasi Ayam
description: A simple yet popular dish consisting of rice served with chicken. The chicken can be prepared in various ways - fried, grilled, or simmered in a flavorful broth. Often served with a side of soup and sambal (chili sauce).

title: Nasi Ayam Bakar
description: This is grilled chicken served with rice. The chicken is marinated in a blend of spices and grilled to perfection, resulting in a smoky and savory flavor. Accompanied by sambal and sometimes a light soup.

title: Nasi Timbel
description: A traditional Sundanese meal that includes steamed rice wrapped in a banana leaf, which imparts a unique aroma. It's typically served with fried chicken, salted fish, tofu, tempeh, and a variety of fresh vegetables.
